                def convert_cm_to_foot(height_value)
          
      149. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    149. 
            
            

            

                  height_data = (height_value / 2.54).round(8)
          
      150. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    150. 
            
            

            

                  height_foot = (height_data / 12).floor
          
      151. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    151. 
            
            

            

                  height_inches = (height_data - (12 * height_foot)).floor
          
      152. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    152. 
            
            

            

                  "#{height_foot}.#{height_inches}"
          
      153. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    153. 
            
            

            

                end
          
      154. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    154.
